<HEADLINE>
U.N. AGENCY IS BRINGING TIMOR ONLINE (HORSEMEN IN MONGOLIA, AS
WELL)
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION NOTICE: Also sent in category ``i'') 
(nk) 
 By WAYNE ARNOLD   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
