and black bars, a new slot machine sports characters from the
popular television show ``South Park.'' Slot machine makers are
turning to popular themes to make betting more entertaining and
appealing for those who are not dedicated gamblers. The trend
worries regulators and critics, who say that these new machines
could appeal to children, worsening the national problem of
underage gambling. By Andrew Pollack.
</P>
